Package: tidysoiltexture
Title: Tidy Tools for Soil Texture Classification and Visualisation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Einar", "Taakefyrsten", , "einaremil1999@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A tidy reimagining of soil texture classification and
    visualisation. Provides pipe-compatible functions that accept and return
    tibbles, with tidy evaluation support for sand, silt, and clay column
    arguments. Implements texture classification according to the USDA system,
    and produces ggplot2-based soil texture triangle plots with sample points,
    continuous fill surfaces, and contour layers. Spatial dispatch methods
    support sf point objects and terra SpatRaster stacks directly.
